127
00:12:42,020 --> 00:12:43,380
and gets carried off

128
00:12:43,420 --> 00:12:45,340
by wild beasts in the wilderness?

129
00:12:46,380 --> 00:12:47,240
How about this?

130
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:48,780
You go back to the capital
to report first.

131
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:49,540
I go check on her.

132
00:12:49,540 --> 00:12:50,340
Yes, General.

133
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:04,260
Miss!

134
00:13:05,340 --> 00:13:06,580
We soldiers on the march

135
00:13:06,580 --> 00:13:08,140
don't carry silver with us.

136
00:13:08,860 --> 00:13:10,560
If you're still trying
to extort money from me,

137
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:12,690
I don't have a single coin left for you.

138
00:13:14,140 --> 00:13:14,820
Miss?

139
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:17,080
Miss?

140
00:13:33,140 --> 00:13:33,940
Miss?

141
00:13:55,460 --> 00:13:56,820
I'm warning you.

142
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:58,800
If you dare to pull that scam again,

143
00:13:58,800 --> 00:13:59,840
I'll kill you.

144
00:14:06,420 --> 00:14:09,380
Uh...

145
00:14:11,860 --> 00:14:13,920
Why do you keep saying "uh" like that?

146
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:16,060
Uh...

147
00:14:16,780 --> 00:14:18,640
What's next? Gonna start a nursery rhyme?

148
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:20,640
Enough. Don't play games with me.

149
00:14:20,700 --> 00:14:21,340
Speak up!

150
00:14:29,060 --> 00:14:29,940
Are you...

151
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:32,240
mute?

152
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,040
I'm sorry, Miss.

153
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:39,710
I didn't know you were mute.

154
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:41,440
How about this?

155
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:42,420
You come back to the state with me.

156
00:14:42,420 --> 00:14:44,480
I'll see to it that you get treatment.

157
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:46,640
So, a fox spirit after all.

158
00:14:55,880 --> 00:14:57,240
My horse!

159
00:15:05,420 --> 00:15:07,220
We'll walk back to the state!

160
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:28,820
After fighting at the border
for half a year,

161
00:15:28,940 --> 00:15:31,820
I thought I'd finally get back
and wash up properly.

162
00:15:32,220 --> 00:15:33,280
But unexpectedly,

163
00:15:33,820 --> 00:15:35,980
I am sleeping
in the wilderness again.

164
00:15:46,100 --> 00:15:47,220
You strange girl,

165
00:15:47,680 --> 00:15:50,140
why do you keep staring at me
with that smile?

166
00:15:54,100 --> 00:15:55,630
I really can't handle this.

167
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:08,400
You...

168
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:10,740
How long has it been since you bathed?

169
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:23,880
I didn't bathe

170
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:25,690
because I didn't have the time.

171
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:27,480
But why didn't you bathe?

172
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:32,930
You're not going

173
00:16:34,040 --> 00:16:36,700
to tell me you have no family or friends,
are you?

174
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:46,820
It's because of the war, isn't it?

175
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:49,560
Now Muxi and Xuanyue

176
00:16:49,560 --> 00:16:51,320
have been at war for a long time.

177
00:16:52,260 --> 00:16:54,500
People are displaced,

178
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:56,260
their families torn apart.

179
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:59,400
I wonder when this war will ever end.

180
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:04,599
Now that we've met,

181
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:05,660
I'd call that fate.

182
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,609
Come back to Muxi State with me.

183
00:17:09,359 --> 00:17:10,420
You can

184
00:17:10,420 --> 00:17:12,079
stay and work in my household.

185
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:15,000
