♪ Wherever you are would be my world ♪

224
00:21:04,700 --> 00:21:05,520
♪ Let the love tribulation fall down ♪

225
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:06,320
Do you like it?

226
00:21:06,560 --> 00:21:07,420
We're home now!

227
00:21:08,180 --> 00:21:08,340
♪ I cast aside my armor ♪

228
00:21:08,340 --> 00:21:09,000
There it is!

229
